    - Initial version in the zef ecosystem

2011-09-25  Kevin Polulak  <kpolulak@gmail.com>
    * Release 0.2.0
    - New subroutines
      + gen_mode_change()
      + matches_mask()
    - Significant improvements in test coverage
      + Verifies public-facing API
    - Improvements in documentation
      + Includes sample code for each subroutine
      + Explains which parameters are optional

2011-08-25  Kevin Polulak  <kpolulak@gmail.com>
    * Release 0.1.1
    - Fixed failed tests in 0.1.0

2011-08-25  Kevin Polulak  <kpolulak@gmail.com>
    * Release 0.1.0
    - First beta release
    - New subroutines
      + parse_mode_line()
      + unparse_mode_line()
    - Improved documentation with examples
    - Better test coverage
    - All tests pass with 1 todo

2011-08-18  Kevin Polulak  <kpolulak@gmail.com>
    * Release 0.0.3
    - New subroutines
      + has_color()
      + has_formatting()
      + normalize_mask()
      + strip_color()
      + strip_formatting()
    - Subroutine strip_formatting() is a little buggy with no tests
    - More documentation
    - Better test coverage
    - All tests pass with 1 todo

2011-08-15  Kevin Polulak  <kpolulak@gmail.com>
    * Release 0.0.2
    - Added name_to_numeric() and numeric_to_name()
    - Full test coverage (all pass)
    - Documentation in perldoc format

2011-08-14  Kevin Polulak  <kpolulak@gmail.com>
